## Connect to SharePoint
Connect-PnPOnline -Url $siteUrl `
    -ClientId $clientId `
    -Tenant $tenantId `
    -CertificatePath $certPath `
    -CertificatePassword $certPassword

Get-PnPWeb | Select Title, Url

